headline: CoStar Group (NasdaqGS:CSGP) Elevates Leadership To Drive European Expansion
summary: CoStar Group (NasdaqGS:CSGP) recently saw a price increase of 11%, coinciding with notable strategic developments, including the appointment of Alexa-Maria Rathbone Barker as Head of CoStar Europe. This executive move aligns with the company's ambition to enhance its European footprint. Additionally, the company's inclusion in several growth benchmarks signifies its strong standing in the market. headline: CoStar Group Names Alexa-Maria Rathbone Barker as Head of CoStar for Europe
summary: LONDON, July 03, 2025--CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP), a global leader in commercial real estate information, analytics, online marketplaces and 3D digital twin technology, today announced the appointment of Alexa-Maria Rathbone Barker as Head of CoStar Europe. This leadership elevation comes as part of the company’s strategic growth plan across Europe.
